data.title: Baystate discography
data.text:
Baystate Records LP discography

Baystate was a Japanese record label that released jazz LPs in the last half of the 1970's and first half of the 1980's. The lists below are incomplete. A number of Baystate releases that are not part of the 6000 or 8000 series will be added at a later date.

Matt Dennis Is Back: Angel Eyes, Matt Dennis, 1979, Baystate RVJ-6026

Tracks : Angel Eyes, Will You Still Be Mine, Love Turns Winter To Sprlng, Never You Mind, The Night We Called It A Day Each Time Is Like The First Time, Violets For Your Furs, Show Me The Way To Get Out Of This World, Everything Happens To Me, Love Is Not For Fools Like Me Let's Get Away From It All, Angel Eyes, There Is A Time In Your Life Before The Show

Musicians : Matt Dennis, Ray Leatherwood, Nick Fatool

Misty Red, Red Garland, 1982, Baystate RJL-8031

Tracks : This Can't Be Love, Misty, But Not For Me, Over The Rainbow, If I Where A Bell, My Funny Valentine, You'd Be So Nice To Come Home To, Willow Weep For Me

Musicians : Red Garland, Jamil Nasser, Frank Gant

Swingin' Love, Kenny Drew Trio, 1983, Baystate RJL-8051

Tracks : But Not For Me, My Romance, Stella By Starlight, Autumn Leaves, Nature Boy, Like Someone In Love, You Don't Know What Love Is, Begin The Beguine, Here's That Rainy Day

Musicians : Kenny Drew, Niels-Henning Orsted Pedersen, Ed Thigpen

Spring Song, Eugen Cicero Trio, 1984, Baystate RJL-8082

Tracks : Prelude No 2 From The Well Tempered Clavier Book 1 (Bach), Caprice No 24 (Paganini), Spinning Song in C (Mendelssohn), The Moldau (Smetena), Spring Song in A major (Mendelssohn), Prelude No. 4 in E minor (Chopin), Air from Orchestral Suite No 3 in D (Bach), Cicero's Paraphrase in G flat (Traditional/Cicero)

Musicians : Eugen Cicero, John Clayton, Billy Higgins

By Request, Kenny Drew, 1985, Baystate RJL-8106

Tracks : Softly, As In A Morning Sunrise, Misty, On Green Dolphin Street, Smoke Gets In Your Eyes, You'd Be So Nice To Come Home To, My Funny Valentine, Lover Come Back To Me, As Time Goes By, Fly Me To The Moon, 'Round Midnight

Musicians : Kenny Drew, Niels-Henning Orsted Pedersen, Ed Thigpen

Sings Again, Chet Baker, 1985, Baystate RJL-8108

Tracks : All Of You, Body And Soul, Look For The Silver Lining, I Can't Get Started, My Funny Valentine, Alone Together, Someone To Watch Over Me, How Deep Is The Ocean

Musicians : Chet Baker, Michel Graillier, Ricardo Del Fra, John Engels

Love Song, Chet Baker, 1987, Baystate RJL-8118

Tracks : I'm A Fool To Want You, You And The Night And The Music, 'Round Midnight, As Time Goes BY, You'd Be So Nice To Come Home To, Angel Eyes, Caravelle

Musicians : Chet Baker, Harold Danko, Jon Burr, Ben Riley
